File permissions:
--------------------
r- Read (4),
w- Write (2),
e- Execute (1).

change permissions:
------------------------
chmod ugo=rwx, g=rw, o=r file_name
 or
chmod ugo=rwx file_name
 or
chmod 764 file_name
 or
chmod u+x, g-w, o=r file_name


changing ownership:
-----------------------
Root user only can change the ownership.

# chown vardhan:vardhan file_name
# chown vardhan file3
